《'''救世主'''》（{{lang-it|Salvator Mundi}}）是[[列奥纳多·达·芬奇|列奥纳多·达·芬奇]]的其中一幅畫作。過去它曾隱沒很長一段時間，甚至一度被認為只是達文西弟子的作品。2004年，[[紐約|紐約]]的羅伯·賽門（Robert Simon）以低價買下該畫作。並交由專家修復與鑑定後，2011年終於重現在世人面前。是一模擬[[肖像畫|肖像畫]]製作的空想作品。

== 歷史 ==
1506年－1513年，達文西接受[[法國國王|法國國王]][[路易十二|路易十二]]的委託，以[[耶穌|耶穌]][[基督|基督]](受膏者)為題繪製這幅畫作。<ref>{{cite web |last=Esterow |first=Milton |url=http://artnews.com/issues/article.asp?art_id=3345 |title=A Long Lost Leonardo |journal=ARTnews |publisher=ARTnews |date=June 2011 |accessdate=2011-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110709120514/http://artnews.com/issues/article.asp?art_id=3345 |archivedate=2011-07-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=BBC News |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-14104031 |title=Lost Leonardo Da Vinci painting to go on show |publisher=BBC |date=12 July 2011 |accessdate=2011-07-12 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116185257/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-14104031 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://en.99ys.com/news/20110701/detail_953.shtml Scholars authenticate a painting that was missing for centuries] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526045552/http://en.99ys.com/news/20110701/detail_953.shtml |date=2013-05-26 }}</ref>

2017年11月15日，[[佳士得|佳士得]]拍賣《救世主》，最終以4.5億[[美元|美元]]（包括手續費）售出，創下單一藝術品的最高拍賣價紀錄。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2017/nov/15/leonardo-da-vinci-salvator-mundi-auction |title=Leonardo da Vinci painting sells for $450m at auction, smashing records |publisher=The Guardian |date=2017-11-16 |accessdate=2017-11-16 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116020536/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2017/nov/15/leonardo-da-vinci-salvator-mundi-auction |dead-url=no }}</ref>买家是沙特王子{{le|巴德尔·本·阿卜杜拉·本·法尔汉|Bader bin Abdullah bin Farhan Al Saud}}。巴德尔此前无艺术收藏，他是沙特王储[[穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特|穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特]]的盟友与朋友。《纽约时报》引述消息人士的话称，《救世主》真正的买家是王储本人。沙特阿拉伯官方否认了这一猜测，表示巴德尔是为阿布扎比王储买下此画。2017年末有报道称这幅画将在[[阿布扎比卢浮宫|阿布扎比卢浮宫]]展出，但原定于2018年9月的揭幕被取消。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The Da Vinci mystery: why is his $450m masterpiece really being kept under wraps?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2018/oct/14/leonardo-da-vinci-mystery-why-is-his-450m-masterpiece-really-being-kept-under-wraps-salvator-mundi|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2018-10-14|accessdate=2020-01-19|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Jonathan|last=Jones|archive-date=2019-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191109181151/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2018/oct/14/leonardo-da-vinci-mystery-why-is-his-450m-masterpiece-really-being-kept-under-wraps-salvator-mundi|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年6月的一份报道称，它被存放在[[穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特|穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼]]的豪华游艇上，等待[[歐拉_(沙特阿拉伯)|欧拉]]文化中心竣工。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Da Vinci's $450 Million Masterpiece Is Kept on Saudi Prince's Yacht: Artnet|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-10/da-vinci-s-450-million-masterpiece-kept-on-mbs-s-yacht-artnet|accessdate=2020-01-19|author=Katya Kazakina|date=|format=|work=www.bloomberg.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2019-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190704143454/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-10/da-vinci-s-450-million-masterpiece-kept-on-mbs-s-yacht-artnet|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年10月，报道称它可能在瑞士收存。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The mystery of the missing Leonardo: where is Da Vinci’s $450m Jesus?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2019/oct/13/leonardo-da-vinci-salvator-mundi-jesus-louvre-exhibition|newspaper=The Observer|date=2019-10-13|accessdate=2020-01-19|issn=0029-7712|language=en-GB|first=Jamie|last=Doward|archive-date=2020-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418063930/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2019/oct/13/leonardo-da-vinci-salvator-mundi-jesus-louvre-exhibition|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 畫作描述 ==
《救世主》與《蒙娜麗莎的微笑》約為同時期之畫作。受法王[[路易十二|路易十二]]所託，畫中穿著寶藍色長袍的[[耶穌基督|耶穌基督]]立於深邃混沌的畫面正中央，左手掌托著代表[[地球|地球]]（Mundi）的水晶球，右手則舉起給予祝福的[[十字聖號|十字聖號]]手勢，象徵將全世界和人類的救贖與福祉捧於掌心。

